atch. Compared to\nexisting methods, we provide provable guarantees on the stability of the\nlearned controllers and extend allowable cost functions to a much larger class.\nSimulations on the 39-bus New England system illustrate our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 May 2022 07:02:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-03"}
